text: The Shebelle River is a river which starts in the Ogadenia region. It flows through the Hirshabelle and Jubaland states of Somalia.Wilson, Thomas H. "Site and settlement patterns of coastal Jubaland, Southern Somalia." Proceedings of the Second International Congress of Somali Studies. Vol. II: Archaeology and History.
